{"title":"秋夜怀人","authors":["宾鹏翔"],"dates":[{"year":1984,"month":2,"day":13}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋夜怀人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宾鹏翔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"卅年离别各西东，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岁月催人近老翁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"入梦几回寻旧雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"相思一夜起秋风。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"情牵扬子江南北，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋届东篱菊紫红。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寂寂有谁同把酒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"倚栏望断去来鸿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（原载《台湾新生报》）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}